<% if @order.purchased_gift_certs? -%>
Gift Certificates
=================
Your have purchased one or more gift certificates. Please pass the following gift certificate code to be redeemed at your next purchase:
<% @order.line_items.select { |li| li.product.is_gift_cert? }.collect { |li| li.coupons }.flatten.each_with_index do |coupon, i| -%>

Gift Certificate #<%= (i+1).to_s %>:
Value: <%= number_to_currency coupon.line_item.price %>
Code: <%= coupon.code %>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
